General.Name: Logistics Development Group PLC
General.Description: Logistics Development Group plc operates as an investment company. It invests in a portfolio of assets. The company was formerly known as Eddie Stobart Logistics plc and changed its name to Logistics Development Group plc in February 2021. Logistics Development Group plc was incorporated in 2014 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
